          <xar:mlstring> Click on Version History tab at the bottom to get the latest release information.</xar:mlstring>
        </li>
        <li><xar:mlstring>Related documentation on Julian can be found at</xar:mlstring> <a href="http://www.xaraya.com/index.php/keywords/julian/" title="#xarML('Related documentation on Julian')#"><xar:mlstring>Xaraya Documentation.</xar:mlstring></a>
        </li>
    </ul>
